<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Update on Your Proposal Submission - <%= title %></title>
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #fff;
      "
    >
      <div style="text-align: center; padding: 30px">
        <img
          src="https://utfs.io/f/7569a78d-1118-40e6-a844-bfc5433fcb83-yko3op.png"
          alt="GFE Logo"
          style="max-width: 150px"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          width: calc(100% - 20px);
          height: 1px;
          background-color: #eee;
          margin: 0 10px;
        "
      ></div>

      <div
        style="
          padding: 20px;
          margin: auto;
          background-color: #fff;
          font-size: 10pt;
        "
      >
        <p>Hello, <%= name %></p>
        <p>
          We want to begin by extending our appreciation for the effort and
          thought you put into your proposal titled
          <a href="<%= link %>"><%= title %></a> Our review team has carefully
          considered your submission. However, after much deliberation, we
          regret to inform you that it has not been approved at this time.
        </p>

        <p>
          Please understand that this decision does not diminish the value of
          your contribution. Our decisions are based on a variety of factors.
        </p>

        <p>
          We encourage you not to be disheartened and invite you to refine and
          resubmit your proposal, or perhaps propose new ideas in the future.
          Should you wish for detailed feedback or guidance on how to strengthen
          your next submission, please donâ€™t hesitate to reach out.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your active participation in our community is highly valued, and we
          look forward to your future contributions.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for your understanding and continuous support.</p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          GFE Foundation Community
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
